Package: com.github.amkay.gradle.git.release.notes.tag.finder

[Groovy] Class VersionTagFinder

    • com.github.amkay.gradle.git.release.notes.tag.finder.VersionTagFinder
    • All Implemented Interfaces and Traits:
      TagFinder

      class VersionTagFinder
extends Object

      This strategy for finding the Git tag of the latest release version is used if the version of the project the plugin was applied on is a normal String. The strategy then searches for a tag matching the version of the project, including the configured GitReleaseNotesPluginExtension.versionPrefix.
